WEBVTT

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:30.176
He and others spread the word
through their congregations

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:31.416
and over the radio.

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:34.135
Municipal government officials
stepped forward and helped

00:08:34.159 --> 00:08:38.336
with permits and with convening
civil society organizations.

00:08:38.360 --> 00:08:41.976
A paint company donated
a thousand liters of yellow paint

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:45.616
mixed especially for us
in what they now call "optimistic yellow."

00:08:45.640 --> 00:08:46.936
(Laughter)

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:52.016
(Applause)

00:08:52.040 --> 00:08:55.296
And a poetry collective
joined forces with a university

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:57.576
and hosted a series of tweet chats

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:59.776
that challenged the nation
on issues of faith,

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:02.456
our faith not just
in the context of religion,